## AI Agent Billing

AI Agents in Harmonic are virtual identities that can navigate the app, create content, make decisions, and run automated tasks on your behalf.

Billing covers the cost of the LLM (language model) calls that power agent reasoning. Your subscription includes:

- A monthly base fee for access
- Usage-based pricing for LLM tokens consumed by your agents

You'll see the exact pricing on the next page before confirming. You can cancel or change your plan at any time.

To set up billing, visit `/billing` in your browser and click "Set Up Billing".
